Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.52,0:22:46.80,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}但又在群里和其他人聊天
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.80,0:22:49.04,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}感觉很近 但其实很远
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.04,0:22:50.60,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}为什么会这么寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.60,0:22:52.68,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}难道他今天不来追我了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.68,0:22:54.62,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}如果能够坦率一点就好了...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.54,0:22:58.20,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(350,350)}毕竟 我也是第一次知道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:01.96,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(350,350)}这是种令人悲伤的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.96,0:23:03.22,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:05.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}为什么要与我背道而行
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.00,0:23:06.74,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}也不告诉我其中的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.74,0:23:09.24,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,350)}这真的很令人焦躁不安
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.38,0:23:12.30,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(350,350)}这种话怎么说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.30,0:23:16.04,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(350,350)}但是刚才这句不是我的心里话
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:17.32,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}告诉我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.32,0:23:19.00,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}你为什么生气了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:20.78,ED-CN,,0,0,0,,{\be4}{\blur5}{\fad(250,250)}是我不够可爱了吗
